1GREG Gregorian The Gregorian calendar is in effect in the most countries of Christian influence since approximately 1582. This calendar superceded the Julian calendar.

concept.definition: The Gregorian calendar is in effect in the most countries of Christian influence since approximately 1582.  This calendar superceded the Julian calendar.
